1.angles are in radians.
2.velocities are in m/s.
3.accelerations are in m/s^2.
4.masses are in kg.
5.distances are in meters.
6.Use local variables unless neccessary
7. For every block code you wirte, figure out a way to test it before integrating into the system.
8. use namespace or don't be lazy with names, when project size grow, name conflicts will be common and the risk of unintentional varible misuse increases.
